              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " You have a concept for an app, a marketplace, or a SaaS tool. You need a working product to show investors or early users — not in 6 months, but in 2-4 weeks. Bubble lets you build a real, functional product that doesn't feel like a prototype.",
