    "image_prompt": "Editorial tech thumbnail, 16:9. Incorporate the brand logo fetched from https://logo.clearbit.com/bubble.io as the clean focal element over a soft amber-to-cream gradient (Notion + Apple aesthetic). A developer sitting at a laptop with a drag-and-drop visual editor on screen, colorful app interface blocks being assembled, coffee mug beside the keyboard, modern minimalist workspace, soft natural lighting. Glassmorphism cards, soft volumetric light, generous negative space for a title, no embedded text, no watermark. --ar 16:9 --style raw",
    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Bubble.io really free to use?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Bubble's free plan includes a development version, API connector, one app editor, 50K workload units per month, and even native mobile editor access with on-device testing. You only upgrade to a paid plan when you're ready to launch and need a custom domain or higher capacity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Bubble apps handle real production traffic?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. Bubble runs on AWS infrastructure and handles scaling automatically. Companies processing thousands of daily users and transactions run on Bubble. You can upgrade your workload unit allocation and server capacity as your app grows.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Do I need any coding experience to use Bubble?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No coding experience is required. Bubble's visual editor lets you design interfaces by dragging elements, set up logic through a visual workflow builder, and manage data through a point-and-click database editor. However, understanding basic concepts like databases, APIs, and conditional logic will help you build more complex apps faster.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
